Commercial Use Restriction

For the purposes of this license, "Commercial Use" includes, but is not
limited to:
- Selling, licensing, or monetizing the software or any derivative work
- Using the software as part of a paid product, service, or offering
- Using the software internally to support revenue-generating activities
- Providing the software to third parties for compensation

Any Commercial Use, including resale or sublicensing, is strictly
prohibited without a separate, explicit, written commercial license
agreement signed by the author.

Unauthorized commercial use constitutes a material breach of this
license and may result in legal action, including claims for damages.